    "## Create a `ProxyDatabase` and load from the pandas `DataFrame`"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 3,
   "id": "3fff69ae-306e-4495-9a4e-af43a6165ff0",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "text/plain": [
       "<cfr.proxy.ProxyDatabase at 0x103aad550>"
      ]
     },
     "execution_count": 3,
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "execute_result"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "pdb = cfr.ProxyDatabase().from_df(df)\n",
    "pdb"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "c1efca55-8b56-452d-b9c3-f07e9b330e4f",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "Once the `ProxyDatabase` is created, we have `ProxyDatabase.records` as a dictionary of `ProxyRecord`."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 4,
   "id": "9cfd1e52-e682-4a11-884b-d39f0e87bd55",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "name": "stdout",
     "output_type": "stream",
     "text": [
      "NAm_153 <cfr.proxy.ProxyRecord object at 0x103aad970>\n",
      "Asi_245 <cfr.proxy.ProxyRecord object at 0x103aadd00>\n",
      "NAm_165 <cfr.proxy.ProxyRecord object at 0x103aadf40>\n",
      "Asi_178 <cfr.proxy.ProxyRecord object at 0x13a453ca0>\n",
      "Asi_174 <cfr.proxy.ProxyRecord object at 0x13a453dc0>\n"
     ]
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "i = 0\n",
    "for pid, pobj in pdb.records.items():\n",
    "    print(pid, pobj)\n",
    "    i += 1\n",
    "    if i >= 5:\n",
    "        break"
   ]
  },

    "## Add several `ProxyRecord`s together to form a `ProxyDatabase`"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 7,
   "id": "20a2cc65-6159-4ff7-b00d-e3103ab78fe3",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "text/plain": [
       "{'NAm_153': <cfr.proxy.ProxyRecord at 0x103aadaf0>,\n",
       " 'Afr_005': <cfr.proxy.ProxyRecord at 0x13efc5550>}"
      ]
     },
     "execution_count": 7,
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "execute_result"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "pdb_sub = pdb.records['NAm_153'] + pdb.records['Afr_005']\n",
    "pdb_sub.records"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "e2cc75a5-505e-4b68-8534-e7c3e3d25b86",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## Add a list of `ProxyRecord`s into an existing `ProxyDatabase`"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 8,
   "id": "e17e42b1-3acc-41c7-8fba-d3b09eb72864",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "text/plain": [
       "{'NAm_153': <cfr.proxy.ProxyRecord at 0x13f212460>,\n",
       " 'Asi_245': <cfr.proxy.ProxyRecord at 0x13f200ac0>,\n",
       " 'NAm_165': <cfr.proxy.ProxyRecord at 0x13eff5640>,\n",
       " 'Asi_178': <cfr.proxy.ProxyRecord at 0x13f008160>,\n",
       " 'Asi_174': <cfr.proxy.ProxyRecord at 0x13a453dc0>}"
      ]
     },
     "execution_count": 8,
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "execute_result"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "pobj_list = list(pdb.records.values())[:5]\n",
    "pdb_sub = cfr.ProxyDatabase()\n",
    "\n",
    "for pobj in pobj_list:\n",
    "    pdb_sub += pobj\n",
    "    \n",
    "pdb_sub.records"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "114bc7e7-0177-465c-8634-766aca22fcb4",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## Merge several `ProxyDatabase`s"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 9,
   "id": "79a4ce73-1a1d-445e-b4fe-a6ee83f57518",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "text/plain": [
       "{'NAm_153': <cfr.proxy.ProxyRecord at 0x13f218220>,\n",
       " 'Asi_245': <cfr.proxy.ProxyRecord at 0x13f218af0>,\n",
       " 'NAm_165': <cfr.proxy.ProxyRecord at 0x13f2181f0>,\n",
       " 'Asi_178': <cfr.proxy.ProxyRecord at 0x13f2263d0>,\n",
       " 'Asi_174': <cfr.proxy.ProxyRecord at 0x13f212310>,\n",
       " 'NAm_102': <cfr.proxy.ProxyRecord at 0x13f218310>,\n",
       " 'NAm_046': <cfr.proxy.ProxyRecord at 0x13f218430>,\n",
       " 'Ocn_065': <cfr.proxy.ProxyRecord at 0x13f218d60>,\n",
       " 'Asi_242': <cfr.proxy.ProxyRecord at 0x13f218a00>,\n",
       " 'Asi_170': <cfr.proxy.ProxyRecord at 0x10449a4c0>}"
      ]
     },
     "execution_count": 9,
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "execute_result"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "pobj_list = list(pdb.records.values())[:5]\n",
    "pdb_sub1 = cfr.ProxyDatabase()\n",
    "for pobj in pobj_list:\n",
    "    pdb_sub1 += pobj\n",
    "        \n",
    "pobj_list = list(pdb.records.values())[10:15]\n",
    "pdb_sub2 = cfr.ProxyDatabase()\n",
    "for pobj in pobj_list:\n",
    "    pdb_sub2 += pobj\n",
    "        \n",
    "pdb_sub = pdb_sub1 + pdb_sub2\n",
    "pdb_sub.records"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "14002055-d389-481d-bafc-2c4c36094bf4",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## Substract a list of `ProxyRecord`s from a `ProxyDatabase`"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 10,
   "id": "6cc677b8-333d-40b3-a462-6dcc03545367",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "text/plain": [
       "{'NAm_102': <cfr.proxy.ProxyRecord at 0x13f23ef70>,\n",

       " 'Ocn_065': <cfr.proxy.ProxyRecord at 0x13f23e9a0>,\n",
       " 'Asi_242': <cfr.proxy.ProxyRecord at 0x13f23edc0>,\n",
       " 'Asi_170': <cfr.proxy.ProxyRecord at 0x13f23ecd0>}"
      ]
     },
     "execution_count": 10,
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "execute_result"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "pdb_left = pdb_sub - pdb_sub1\n",
    "pdb_left.records"
   ]
  },

    "## Convert a `ProxyRecord` to an `xarray.DataArray`"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "id": "eb71e71c-5095-4e88-ad58-1102b97a2d10",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "text/html": [
       "<div><svg style=\"position: absolute; width: 0; height: 0; overflow: hidden\">\n",
       "<defs>\n",
